## Overview

This repository contains my hands-on cybersecurity labs and practical exercises performed in a controlled virtual lab environment using Kali Linux and Ubuntu.

The goal is to develop real-world skills in:

* Network scanning
* Service enumeration
* Linux system analysis
* Penetration testing fundamentals

